Certain aspects of the present disclosure generally relate to
wireless communications. In some aspects, a device may
determine a peak to average ratio (PAR) value for a portion
of a wireless transmission. In some aspects, the device may
cause, based on the PAR value, a voltage to be applied to a
power amplifier of the device to cause the device to transmit
the portion of the wireless transmission.
